---
title: Persian-Inspired Chickpea and Chicken Stew with Toasted Garlic Flatbreads
description: Middle Eastern spice-roasted carrots are the star of this warming tomato-based chicken stew. Toasted almonds and a spicy chili-garlic sauce are the perfect toppers for this crave-worthy dinner!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/persian-inspired-chickpea-and-chicken-stew-ce0cd8aa-6447d7b1.jpg
